{"tid":1589873,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)強戰世界 黑魔塔 生力啤Running Man","createTime":"2019-09-23T12:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T17:59:36.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1b453f514cc4a636a286266ee2f6b8e4fddf391b","tid":1589873,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:47:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK60n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=60c469ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK60n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=f6fb2437\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK60n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=9bc03faa\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.movie2free.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/WaroftheWorlds.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.movie2free.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2FWaroftheWorlds.jpg&h=0b222c10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9a/The_Dark_Tower_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9a%2FThe_Dark_Tower_Poster.jpg&h=d22264de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/ee/Running_Man_Theatrical_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fee%2FRunning_Man_Theatrical_Poster.jpg&h=53e35ac9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一架巨型的三腳戰機由地面爆出，並瞬間摧毀了附近的一切，現場頓成人間地獄&hellip;&hellip;原來是火星人想攻佔地球，所以製造一場毀滅地球的浩劫！ Ray（湯姆&middot;克魯斯飾）帶著兒女逃走，這時他才發現保護家人是他唯一的生存職責，為了保護家人安全，Ray縱使自知力量微小，也要和強大的外星人軍隊對抗！<br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述在文明崩壞世界中，羅蘭&middot;德斯欽是名主要以雙左輪手槍為武器的僅存槍客，他希望能在宇宙的中樞「黑塔」找到阻止自己世界滅亡的方法<br />\n<br />\n3.2017年，全球經濟已經崩潰，美國社會也變成了一個極權主義警察國家，所有的文化活動都會受到嚴格審查。政府通過播放一個名為《逃跑的人》的真人電視節目來轉移公眾注意力，製造和諧社會的假象。這個節目的主要內容就是將被定罪的重刑犯流放到一個廢棄的城區，然後派出多位職業殺手前往追殺，聲稱只要罪犯能夠制服甚至殺死所有派出的殺手，就可以獲得自由的大獎，通過這種以暴制暴性質的節目來舒緩民眾心中的不滿。這個節目由一位名叫達蒙&middot;基里安（Damon Killian，理察&middot;道森飾）的人主持<br />\n<br />\n9 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK60n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=851524a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK60n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=332c5e1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b854a55b1e6ac0843c64a627d24aaa46af2ad8e7","tid":1589873,"uid":4760